wer in adversity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 13, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever would like for Allah to answer him during times of hardship and difficulty, let him supplicate often during times of ease.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3382 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32003,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/13\/awwal-jannah-al-hamidun\/","url_meta":{"origin":35071,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: Paradise for praising Allah in every circumstance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 13, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe first to be called to Paradise are those who always praised Allah in times of prosperity and adversity.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 12345 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5264,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/18\/sabr-tested-prosperity\/","url_meta":{"origin":35071,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Awf on Sabr: We were tested with prosperity, and we failed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 18, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Zuhri reported: Abdur Rahman ibn Awf, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cWe were tested with hardship alongside the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and we were patient. Then, we were tested with prosperity afterwards and we were not patient.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2464 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36593,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/06\/06\/obedience-usri-yusra\/","url_meta":{"origin":35071,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Sultan: Obey authorities in prosperity and adversity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 6, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cYou must listen and obey authorities in hardship and ease, what you are eager for and what you dislike, even if they give undue preference over you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1836 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"